    <refsection id="Description_INIMPL_f">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            This block represent an implicit input port. It must only be used inside a Xcos Super Block
            and be connected to an implicit input in the subsystem.
        </para>
        <para>
            This block is a signal link from outside of a system into a sub-system. In a Super Block, the implicit's input ports must be numbered from 1 to the total number of implicit's input ports.
            You can set it with the <emphasis role="bold">Port number</emphasis> parameter.
        </para>
    </refsection>
